ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAGREEMENT - Bring into force Aruba FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Kingdom of the Netherlands in respect of ARUBA FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS, signed on 20 October 2011.
